{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b (HOW TO START)}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 If you are reading this chapter, you are standing at the beginning of something important.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Perhaps you woke up this morning with the familiar weight of regret. Perhaps you made another promise to yourself last night\u8221"\u8221"{\i this time will be different}\u8221"\u8221"and you already feel the doubt creeping in.\par}
