{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b YOUR FIRST ENTRY}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Open your Field Journal to the first page. Write today\u8217's date. Write:\par}
