{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 That is all. No grand proclamations. No dramatic promises. Just the simple, honest fact of your presence.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Below that, write one sentence answering this question:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li720 \fi0 {\b What brought me here?}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Be honest. No one will read this but you.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\i \u8220"I drank again last night after I swore I wouldn\u8217't.\u8221"}\par}
