{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\i \u8220"I cannot stop scrolling even when I know it is destroying me.\u8221"}\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This is not a confession for punishment. This is {\i reconnaissance}. You are gathering intel on your own situation. A captain cannot navigate without knowing where the ship currently is.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b THE FIRST PROTOCOL}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Today, you have only one mission: {\b Do not harm the vessel.}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 You do not need to be perfect. You do not need to overhaul your life by sunset. You only need to get through today without making things worse.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 If you usually drink six beers, drink five. If you usually scroll until 2 AM, stop at 1 AM. If you usually skip the gym, just put on the shoes\u8221"\u8221"you do not need to go, just put them on.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Progress is not perfection. Progress is {\i direction}.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b A WORD ABOUT COMPASSION}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 You may have picked up this book expecting to be yelled at. Boot camp for the brain. \u8220"Tough love\u8221" that is mostly tough and very little love.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 That is not what this is.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Yes, we will be direct. Yes, we will tell you hard truths. But we will tell them with the care of someone who wants you to succeed, not the contempt of someone who thinks you are weak.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 You have probably already beaten yourself up enough for several lifetimes. How is that working?\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This manual is built on a different premise: {\b You are not the enemy. You are the patient {\i and} the physician.}\par}
