{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b (SANCTUARY & VISUAL NOISE)}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 A ship\u8217's bridge is the command center\u8212-the place where the Operator has the clearest view and the most control.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 In your life, the Bridge is your {\b environment}. And whether you realize it or not, your environment is constantly steering you.\par}
