{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 We do what is easy. We avoid what is hard. Therefore:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Make good behaviors frictionless\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Make bad behaviors high-friction\sa180\par}
