) is phone-free.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Morning First Hour:} No phone for the first 60 minutes after waking (or until after your Morning Watch).\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Zone 2: Time Blocks}\par}
