{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Limerence (obsessive attraction) is not love; it is the ignition system for love\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Healthy relationships are two complete ships sailing in formation, not two incomplete halves merging\par}
