{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab What I will do differently next time:\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This is not punishment. This is data. You are studying the ship for weaknesses.\par}
