{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 APPENDIX: MEDEVAC\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b (WHEN TO SEEK PROFESSIONAL HELP)}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This book is a field manual, not a hospital.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 There are conditions beyond self-help. Recognizing when you need professional reinforcement is not weakness\u8212-it is operational wisdom.\par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 IMMEDIATE MEDEVAC (Emergency Services)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Call emergency services (911 in the US) if:}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab You are actively planning to harm yourself or someone else\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab You have access to means (weapons, pills) and a plan\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab You are experiencing a psychotic break (hallucinations, severe dissociation from reality)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab You have harmed yourself and need medical attention\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab You are in physical danger\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b This is not the time for self-help. This is the time for immediate intervention.}\par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 24/7 CRISIS LINES\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Keep these accessible. Add them to your phone now, before you need them.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 United States\par}
