{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b SAMHSA National Helpline:} 1-800-662-4357 (substance abuse)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Veterans Crisis Line:} 988 (press 1)\sa180\par}
